data.description: This beautiful colonial is centrally located in the quaint town of Louisa. This spacious home has a lot to offer with beautiful hardwoods, a formal dining room, a room used for a formal sitting room/office/playroom (endless possibilities), powder room, a spacious living area and kitchen. Upstairs there are 4 generous size bedrooms, 1 full shared bath and of course a beautiful en-suite. The en-suite bath has both a soaking tub and stand alone shower along with double sinks. There is tons of closet space throughout the entire home and with the washer and dryer hook ups centrally located upstairs, there is no lugging laundry down flights of stairs. Outside in the backyard enjoy an area to grill and entertain in the warmer months. The spacious attached 2 car garage and the paved driveway are huge pluses out front.  Shopping, pharmacies, restaurants & grocery  just 5 minutes away. Close to 64 for commuters. Xfinity available! This home is a must see!
